---
pagination:
  data: collections.event
  size: 6
  reverse: true
permalink: "/{% if pagination.pageNumber > 0 %}page/{{ pagination.pageNumber + 1 }}/{% endif %}"
---

{% extends 'page.njk' %}

{% block body %}

  <h2>Welcome!</h2>
  <p>Full Stack DFW is an online-first tech-enthusiast group serving folks around the Dallas Fort Worth metroplex who are interested in full stack development.</p>
  <p>We host online learning lunches on the second Wednesday of the month at 12:30 PM CT on our Discord server, linked below.</p>
  <p>Join us, won't you?</p>

  <h2 class="mt-8 mb-4">Upcoming Events</h2>
  <iframe width="100%" class="mx-auto" src="https://calendar.google.com/calendar/embed?height=300&wkst=1&bgcolor=%23ffffff&ctz=America%2FChicago&showTitle=0&showNav=0&showDate=0&mode=AGENDA&showPrint=0&showTabs=0&showCalendars=0&showTz=0&title=Full%20Stack%20DFW&src=MW05bzhtOGQ3aGMwOTk1bXNmZmRjYjBuaTZjN3B2YjJAaW1wb3J0LmNhbGVuZGFyLmdvb2dsZS5jb20&color=%234285F4" style="border-width:0" width="325" height="300" frameborder="0" scrolling="no"></iframe>

  <h2 class="mt-12 mb-4">Previous Events</h2>
  <ol class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 mb-4">
  {%- for event in collections.event | reverse -%}
    <li >
      <h3><time>{{ event.data.date | dateDisplay }}</time></h3>
      <h4><a href="{{ event.url }}">{{ event.data.title }}</a></h4>
      <h4>{{event.data.speaker }}</h4>
    </li>
  {%- endfor -%}
  </ol>

  <p class="block text-center text-sm"> If you are interested in speaking, please fill out <a href="https://forms.gle/PaXtDD4DRK976pF86">this form</a>.</p>


{% endblock %}
